Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.46,0:21:12.95,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.13,0:21:26.02,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}大丈夫　一人だっていいけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.74,0:21:33.19,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}本当はね　誰も一人じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.19,0:21:39.37,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}幸せが　寂しさが　不安も
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.78,0:21:48.91,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}全部味わうために生まれた
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.75,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}一匙のきらめきで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.88,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}微笑みに変えていく
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.88,0:22:02.68,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}それは密かに願い込めた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.68,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}奇跡かも
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.93,0:22:12.65,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}一番大事な宝物を
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.94,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}見つけていくことが僕らの旅
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.94,0:22:25.67,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.15,0:22:34.21,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}目の前の今を希望で紡ぐよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.46,0:21:12.95,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.13,0:21:26.02,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}沒關係  一個人也能過得很好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.74,0:21:33.19,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}但其實  沒有人是孤獨的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.19,0:21:39.37,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}幸福  寂寞  擔憂
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.78,0:21:48.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}都是人生的必由之路
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.75,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}一小匙的閃耀
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.88,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便能化為一抹微笑
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.88,0:22:02.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}或許那是悄悄埋下的願望
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}讓奇蹟綻放
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.93,0:22:12.65,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}將那最最重要的寶物找到
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.94,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便是我們此行的目標
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.94,0:22:25.67,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.15,0:22:34.21,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}也要用希望編織當下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:12.95,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:26.02,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}大丈夫　一人だっていいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:33.19,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}本当はね　誰も一人じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:39.37,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}幸せが　寂しさが　不安も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:48.91,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}全部味わうために生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.75,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一匙のきらめきで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.88,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}微笑みに変えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:22:02.68,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}それは密かに願い込めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.68,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}奇跡かも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:12.65,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一番大事な宝物を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.94,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}見つけていくことが僕らの旅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:25.67,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:34.21,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}目の前の今を希望で紡ぐよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:12.95,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:26.02,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}沒關係  一個人也能過得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:33.19,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}但其實  沒有人是孤獨的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:39.37,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}幸福  寂寞  擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:48.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}都是人生的必由之路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.75,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一小匙的閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.88,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便能化為一抹微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:22:02.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}或許那是悄悄埋下的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.68,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}讓奇蹟綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:12.65,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}將那最最重要的寶物找到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.94,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便是我們此行的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:25.67,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}雖不知能走多遠
